  <acronym>TAUBER</acronym>
  <official_title>GH Therapy in Partial GHD Adolescents : Evaluation of Efficacy Based on Body Composition and Comparison of 2 Different Doses of GenotonormÂ®. Open-Label, Randomised, Comparative, Controlled, Parallel-Group, Multi-Center Phase IIIB Clinical Trial.</official_title>
